ing your skills in a high-pressure scenario.\n\n\nWhether you're a healthcare professional or a concerned citizen, Illuminant CPR Training offers an engaging and effective way to master essential CPR skills. Download now and be prepared to save lives with confidence!", "short_description": "Learn life saving skills!"}]}, "developer_name": "Illuminant Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://illuminantincvr.wixsite.com/mysite/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Illuminant Inc", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://illuminantincvr.wixsite.com/mysite", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "27659109213687786"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "489533950659066"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "489533950659066"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1726680720, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "489533950659066"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "27607478988850809", "version": "1.4"}, "id": "496728726609776", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "27607215812210460